show.title: Mr. Billionaire's heart is mine

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: When fiery Maya Sinha crosses paths with ruthless billionaire lawyer Sameer Malhotra, sparks fly. Between betrayal by her ex Raj and her fight to save her father, Maya discovers that the cold-hearted tycoon’s guarded heart may just belong to her. Watch Now!
